changelog:
Paris Update
- PARIS: Rewrites mod to no longer use various (old) Lighting Ultimate files. Removes 2016 vanilla lighting.
- PARIS - DAY: Gives daytime more realistic, less saturated look, changes sun position, fixes post filter settings in some dark basement rooms
- PARIS – NIGHT: More lamps turned on in some spots
- PARIS – HOLIDAY HOARDERS: Sets to foggy blue night to differentiate from regular night more
- REMOVES TEST OFFLINE CONTRACTS
